parameters.name: ClusterId
parameters.description: The ID of the Container Service for Kubernetes (ACK) cluster. This parameter is required when the ClusterType parameter is set to ask or one.

parameters.name: ClusterType
parameters.description: The cluster type. Valid values: ask, ecs, and one.

parameters.name: ResourceGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the resource group to which the Prometheus instance belongs.

parameters.name: VpcId
parameters.description: The ID of the virtual private cloud (VPC) where the cluster resides.
